<plot>What better way to give a long-overdue tribute to the 3 Stooges than by giving them their own "mock" awards show. Hosted by Martin Short, this hilarious look at the geniuses of comedy combines everything you could want from great clips to never-before-seen home movies, to the ultimate award given to the Stooges a massive pie fight involving the entire awards' show audience.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?595893</url></doc>
